import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class Timeline extends Component { render() { return (
highlights

Timeline

Internship at SoftServe IT Academy 2019-present

I recently have joined the SoftServe as a Software Developer in the DevOps team. My major part of the work has been into the field of creating sustainable and flexible CI/CD (Continuous Integration & Continuous Development) pipelines which enables developers at my team to do rapid development. I am also exploring the role of container technology like Docker and container-orchrastation technologies like Kubernetes and Openshift to create industry standard production environments.

Graduated from NU LP2018-2019

I am pursuing my under-graduation studies with major in C.S.N.T.(Computer Systems Networing & Telecommunications). I have taken courses like OOPs, Computer Networks, IOT, Web-Data Management over the years and have better understanding of these subjects.

Primary and Higher Education 2014-2017

I have completed my higher secondary education with major subjects as Networks and Telecomunications. During my time at school, I have developed interest in solving complex problems of the fundamental math which helped me to improve my understanding of any problems to actually solve this problems.
